  Release Description:
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

   Microsoft VirtualEarth Hybrid Downloader is a cute tool that help you to 
   get small tile hybrid images from Microsoft VirtualEarth. All downloaded 
   small images are saved on the disk. You can view downloaded maps by Map 
   Viewer Or you can combine them into a big BMP map. It supports proxy 
   server. And you can easily get the longitude and latitude of each 
   downloaded small tile image.
